<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> Ai and services</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Custom CSS for styling the page */
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .main-section {
            margin: 50px 0;
        }

        .production-title {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .production-text {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #495057;
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-text {
            text-align: justify;
        }

        /* Keyframe animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-30px);
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .d-flex {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .section-text {
            margin-left: 30px;
            max-width: 400px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-family: ui-monospace;
        }

        .card {
            width: 300px;
        }

        /* Animation for images */
        .animated-image {
            animation: slideIn 1s ease forwards;
        }
        .card-text{
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar1') %>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="container main-section">
        <h1 class="production-title">Services and AI</h1>

        <h3 class="section-title">1. Artificial Intelligence</h3>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img id="image1" src="/static/services11.webp" class="card-img-top animated-image" alt="">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">AI</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="section-text">
                AI-Powered Robots: Robots equipped with AI and machine learning algorithms can perform complex tasks,
                such as assembly, welding, and painting, with greater precision and speed than traditional automation
                systems. These robots can adapt to new tasks through learning.
                AI enables collaborative robots to work alongside humans safely.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="section-title">2. Autonomous Driving</h3>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start engine-production-container">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img id="image2" src="/static/services12.jpg" class="card-img-top animated-image" alt="">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Ai is Future</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="section-text">
                Autonomous vehicles rely on AI to interpret data from sensors, cameras, and radar to navigate safely. AI
                algorithms help vehicles detect obstacles, recognize traffic signs, and make real-time decisions,
                enabling self-driving cars to function without human intervention.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="section-title">3. Predictive Maintenance</h3>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start final-assembly-container">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img id="image6" src="/static/services13.jpg" class="card-img-top animated-image" alt="">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Schematic of Ai</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="section-text">
                Predictive maintenance in automobiles, powered by artificial intelligence (AI), uses data from vehicle
                sensors to monitor performance and predict potential issues before they occur. AI algorithms analyze
                patterns in the data to forecast when parts, such as brakes, engines, or batteries, might fail or need
                servicing.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="section-title">4. Maintenance</h3>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start manufacturing-container">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img id="image3" src="/static/servicesm.jpg" class="card-img-top animated-image" alt="">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Engine diagnostics</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="section-text">
                Maintenance of automobile services involves regular inspections, repairs, and replacements to ensure
                vehicles operate efficiently and safely. Key tasks include oil changes, tire rotations, brake
                inspections, fluid checks, and engine diagnostics. Proper maintenance extends the life of a vehicle,
                improves fuel efficiency, and prevents costly breakdowns.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="section-title">5. Customization</h3>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start engine-production-container">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img id="image4" src="/static/services15c.jpg" class="card-img-top animated-image" alt="">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Custom paint jobs</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="section-text">
                Customization of automobile services allows owners to personalize their vehicles according to their
                preferences and needs. This can include aesthetic changes like custom paint jobs, interior upgrades, or
                performance enhancements such as engine tuning, suspension modifications, and the installation of
                specialized components.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="section-title">6. Body-repairs</h3>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start testing-container">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img id="image5" src="/static/servicesb.jpg" class="card-img-top animated-image" alt="">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Bodywork & Collision Repair</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="section-text">
                Accidents happen. Our skilled technicians handle everything from minor scratches to major collision
                repairs.
                These repairs can include fixing dents, scratches, and rust, as well as replacing damaged panels,
                bumpers, or windshields. Skilled technicians use specialized tools and techniques, such as paint
                matching and precision welding.
            </p>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/footer1') %>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
